Rating: 2
Quite good and satisfies the lemon craving but I've had better lemon pie/tart recipes. The crust was a hassle with all its steps but had a nice taste and texture (like shortbread). The crust was also quite thick. The lemon filling was not too tart but not too sweet. It really didn't set properly until the second day and I cooked it until if was very thick. Good but not great.

